 can be solved by exotic tile assembly models from the literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 2015 21:32:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Jul 2016 00:58:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-01"}
