. We apply a partial correlation coefficient to the new\nde-evolved luminosities showing that the intrinsic correlation exists.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Jun 2015 23:16:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-06"}
